# Template Overrides
# ==================
# List files here that your app has customized and should NOT be overwritten
# by template updates. Use exact file paths (no directories or globs).
#
# Example:
#   frontend/src/api/client.ts
#   frontend/src/components/Shell.tsx
#   docs/getting-started.md
#
# These files exist in .template-manifest but your app needs custom versions.
# The update-from-template tool will skip these files during sync.
